5. Supported Networks

Clarinet lets you target different execution environments:

Network	Description
simnet	Ultra-fast, lightweight local network for unit testing.
devnet	Docker-based local Stacks + Bitcoin nodes for full integration tests.
testnet	Public pre-production network for realistic testing.
mainnet	Live Stacks blockchain for production contracts.

Each network serves a distinct stage in development and deployment. 
